OL,3,CThree more charged following violence
OL,4,Csparked by Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FHampshire Police say three more people
OL,7,Fhave been charged following violent
OL,8,Fdisorder in Southampton on Tuesday
OL,9,Fevening.
OL,11,FDarren Medhurst, 36, of Carnation
OL,12,FRoad, Southampton, Jordan Hambleton,
OL,13,F19, of Rollesbrook Gardens,
OL,14,FSouthampton and Callum Darch, 27, of
OL,15,FSt Blaize Road, Romsey, have all been
OL,16,Fremanded into custody after being
OL,17,Fcharged with violent disorder.
OL,19,FThey are due to appear at Southampton
OL,20,FMagistrates' Court tomorrow (8 June).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
