OL,3,CThree more charged following violence
OL,4,Csparked by Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FEleven Hampshire police officers and a
OL,12,Fpolice dog were injured as missiles
OL,13,Fincluding wheelie bins and chairs were
OL,14,Fthrown during protests organised in
OL,15,Fresponse to the murder of student
OL,16,FHenry Nowak.
OL,18,FIn total, 14 people have so far been
OL,19,Fcharged in connection with the unrest
OL,20,Fin the Portswood area of Southampton.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
