PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780920676
OL,3,CThree more charged following violence
OL,4,Csparked by Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FYesterday, four men pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fcharges of violent disorder.
OL,9,FHarry Varney, 34, of Briarswood,
OL,10,FSouthampton; Taylor Grundy, 22, of
OL,11,FGosport; Dillon Crawford, 29, of
OL,12,FWilton Avenue, Southampton; and Andrew
OL,13,FSummerhayes, 38, of Banning Street,
OL,14,FRomsey, appeared at Southampton
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court.
OL,17,FThey all admitted violent disorder,
OL,18,Fand Summerhayes also pleaded guilty to
OL,19,Ftwo counts of possessing an offensive
OL,20,Fweapon in a public place.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
