PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780920676
OL,3,CThree more charged following violence
OL,4,Csparked by Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FProsecutor Robert Salame told the
OL,7,Fcourt Crawford allegedly used "large
OL,8,Fitems including bins and chairs"
OL,9,Fagainst police officers, while
OL,10,FSummerhayes was said to have thrown
OL,11,Fitems at police officers.
OL,13,FVarney was accused of refusing to move
OL,14,Fwhen asked to by officers, and pushing
OL,15,Fagainst their shields, the court heard.
OL,17,FGrundy was also accused of wheeling a
OL,18,F"large, industrial bin" in the
OL,19,Fdirection of police officers, Salame
OL,20,Fsaid.
