PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780920676
OL,3,CThree more charged following violence
OL,4,Csparked by Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FReeves is accused of using "a traffic
OL,7,Fcone and other large objects" against
OL,8,Fpolice during the protest, the court
OL,9,Fwas told, while Riddett allegedly spat
OL,10,Fat an officer and was aggressive.
OL,12,FHe is also accused of encouraging
OL,13,Fothers to be violent against the
OL,14,Fpolice during the protest, the court
OL,15,Fheard.
OL,17,FReeves and Riddett were also remanded
OL,18,Fin custody to appear at Southampton
OL,19,FCrown Court on Wednesday.
