PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780920676
OL,3,CThree more charged following violence
OL,4,Csparked by Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FThe treatment of the teenager
OL,7,Ftriggered a political row, with the
OL,8,FPrime Minister urging politicians to
OL,9,Fheed the teenager's relatives' calls
OL,10,Fnot to use the case "to cause
OL,11,Fdisturbances".
OL,13,FViolent protests erupted near where
OL,14,Fthe student was fatally stabbed.
OL,16,FDigwa had claimed to police he had
OL,17,Fbeen the victim of a racial attack,
OL,18,Fwhile Nowak was handcuffed by officers
OL,19,Fwho ignored his pleas he could not
OL,20,Fbreathe as he lay dying.
